{"id":"D4AF826E2C90CF12315CAC9D6FF88631","title":"谁在引导我们消费","type":"揭露","content":"我们为什么要买东西？谁让这个世界变得无节制消费？他们如何做到这一点？调查记者雅克·佩雷蒂审视了无节制消费潮流背后的机制，得出了答案。","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nahzur-h/Movie/master/json/api/image/made-us-spend.png","logo":"","timestamp":1588679282798,"introduceList":[{"type":1000,"text":"我们为什么要买东西？谁让这个世界变得无节制消费？他们如何做到这一点？调查记者雅克·佩雷蒂审视了无节制消费潮流背后的机制，得出了答案。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nahzur-h/Movie/master/json/api/image/made-us-spend01.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"原来，使这个世界变得无节制消费的元凶，并不是人们普遍认为的广告员和市场推广员，而是这诸多因素背后那些首先改变产品然后改变我们的人们。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"纪录片表明，长久以来，制造商都梦想着在消费者大脑中植入“升级”观念，从而让无限消费成为现实。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nahzur-h/Movie/master/json/api/image/the-men-who-made-us-spend-001.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"他们首先瞄准未被开发的儿童市场，学习应用向儿童销售的方法，从而增加向成年人的销售。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"但是，那头最肥的能够带来现金的奶牛却来自恐惧——通过挖掘消费者的恐惧，制造商发现了一个对健康和安全产品有巨大需求的世界。","image":""}],"videoList":[{"title":"第一集","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nahzur-h/Movie/master/json/api/image/the-men-who-made-us-spend-002.jpg","m3u8Url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nahzur-h/Movie/master/home/the-men-who-made-us-spend-01/playlist.m3u8"},{"title":"第二集","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nahzur-h/Movie/master/json/api/image/the-men-who-made-us-spend-003.jpg","m3u8Url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nahzur-h/Movie/master/home/the-men-who-made-us-spend-02/playlist.m3u8"},{"title":"第三集","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nahzur-h/Movie/master/json/api/image/the-men-who-made-us-spend-004.jpg","m3u8Url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nahzur-h/Movie/master/home/the-men-who-made-us-spend-03/playlist.m3u8"}]}